      <title>美国官员就中国芯片限制向荷兰政府施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-officials-to-pressure-dutch-government-on-china-chip-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着拜登政府加大力度挫败北京的科技野心，美国高级官员将于本月晚些时候访问荷兰，向荷兰政府施压，要求其加强对中国芯片设备的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/us-officials-to-pressure-dutch-government-on-china-chip-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 14:15:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
