    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯在哈尔科夫致命袭击后瞄准权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ukraine-says-four-killed-in-russian-drone-attack-on-kharkiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯军队一夜之间加大了对乌克兰第二大城市的攻击力度，这是最近针对该国电力基础设施的行动的一部分，此次攻击的强度超过了去年类似的攻击强度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ukraine-says-four-killed-in-russian-drone-attack-on-kharkiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 06:29:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
